INSERT INTO user_sessions (id, user_id, refresh_token, expires_at)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         user_id as "user_id!: Uuid",
                         refresh_token,
                         expires_at as "expires_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                         created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
